<p>Red Dead Revolver was originally a Capcom game developed by Angel Studios in the US, with chara designs by Akiman. The game had a troubled production &amp; remained unplayable until Rockstar bought it from Capcom &amp; finished it. Today it's one of the best selling game franchises ever!</p>
